WEBVTT

00:01:29.097 --> 00:01:32.378
accommodating a wide range
of beliefs, origins, customs,

00:01:32.402 --> 00:01:33.585
goods, food.

00:01:34.315 --> 00:01:35.480
How did my country --

00:01:35.504 --> 00:01:38.202
a country with communities
living harmoniously together

00:01:38.226 --> 00:01:40.717
and comfortable in discussing
their differences --

00:01:40.741 --> 00:01:44.826
how did it degenerate into civil war,
violence, displacement

00:01:44.850 --> 00:01:47.755
and unprecedented sectarian hatred?

00:01:48.239 --> 00:01:51.047
There were many reasons
that had led to the war --

00:01:51.071 --> 00:01:53.156
social, political and economic.

00:01:53.743 --> 00:01:55.307
They all have played their role.

00:01:55.331 --> 00:01:59.203
But I believe there is one key reason
that has been overlooked

00:01:59.227 --> 00:02:01.137
and which is important to analyze,